org.cripac.isee.alg.pedestrian.attr

Interface Recognizer

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DeepMAR, DeepMARCaffe2
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DeepMARCaffe2Native, ExternRecognizer, FakeRecognizer

    public interface Recognizer
    The Recognizer class is the base class of all pedestrian attribute recognizing classes. Any subclass is required to implement a simple 'recognize' method, which takes in a track and returns an attribute.
    Author:
    Ken Yu, CRIPAC, 2016
